            "id": 6009902,
            "title": "南韓李在明談就職首日：總統府像墓地一樣",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>韓國總統李在明 4 日正式開啟總統任期，前往首爾龍山總統府履職。談到就職首日，他稱總統府「空無一物、像墓地一樣」，因前政府未作交接，那裡沒有電腦、網路、印表機。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009902%2Fl%2F0301702944f38b89517941ff8fc54605.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">南韓李在明談就職首日：總統府像墓地一樣。（圖：REUTERS/TPG）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>與過去不同，本次大選是在總統缺位情況下所舉行，因此沒有前任總統與當選總統交接的流程，當選總統在選舉結果正式確定後立即履職。根據韓國媒體報導，前總統尹錫悅去年 12 月遭國會彈劾後，龍山總統府已停止運作。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>李在明在龍山總統府告訴記者：「我剛來到這裡，這裡像墓地一樣，什麼都沒有，甚至沒有工作人員拿東西讓我寫寫。沒有電腦，也沒有印表機。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>韓國總統秘書室發言人姜由楨表示，就職首日就開始工作「在物理上是不可能的」，因為府內缺少網路、紙筆等基礎設施和辦公設備，前政府未留下關於交接的只言片語。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>姜由楨指出，政府各部門先前曾派人到總統府工作，尹錫悅被彈劾後，這些人已回到原部門。李在明上任後，下令這些人員重返總統府工作。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>李在明競選期間表示，他只是暫時在龍山總統府辦公，在青瓦台重新裝修後，將把總統府遷回青瓦台。從長遠來看，他將推動把總統府遷往世宗市。根據韓國媒體說法，總統府預計在 6 個月內搬回青瓦台。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>李在明組成新內閣仍需數週時間，原因是內閣提名人選須接受國會聽證會。尹錫悅任命的全體內閣成員已於 2 日集體遞交辭呈，但李在明 4 日未予批准，僅接受法務部長官樸性載的辭呈。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>姜由楨說，李在明此舉意在保證國政運作的持續性。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
